         <td class="mid_panel"> <h3>Our Vision</h3> <p> Providing and training for University of Colombo undergraduates to embark on an optimal career and develop the necessary transferable skills including attitude, motivation and skills necessary to become efficient members of the workforce.</p></td> 
         <td><img src="images/home_pic2.jpg" width="334" height="190"></td> 
        </tr> 
        <tr> 
         <td colspan="2" class="hot_panel"> <h2>Hot News- <strong>Career Fair 2005</strong></h2> <p><strong><a href="events_careerfair2005.htm">Career Fair 2005</a> </strong>is to be held on the 28th of November 2005. The event aims to provide an opportunity for the prospective employees to meet the employers and to explore potential career opportunities. During the event, the employers have an opportunity to meet the final year undergraduates who will be passing out within the next couple of months as well as those who have recently graduated. Over 1000 job seekers from several disciplines including Science, Management and Finance, Law, Arts, Education will be participating in the event.</p> </td> 
